Class Definition

java.lang.Object
  de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.model.core.Definition
All Implemented Interfaces:
IHasTextRepresentations, java.lang.Comparable<Definition>
public class Definition
extends java.lang.Object
implements IHasTextRepresentations, java.lang.Comparable<Definition>

Definition is a class representing a narrative description of a Sense. It is displayed for human users to facilitate their understanding of the meaning of a LexicalEntry.
Instances of Definition class are also used for narrative description of a SemanticArgument instance.

Author:
Zijad Maksuti
